Basically it transforms endorsment policies [https://hyperledger-fabric.readthedocs.io/en/release-1.4/endorsement-policies.html] from string format to python dict and the opposite way.
policy declared like `{{OR('Org1.member', 'Org2.member')}}` will be transformed as:

 

{{```
 {        'identities': [
            { 'role': { 'name': 'member', 'mspId': 'Org1' }},
            { 'role': { 'name': "member', 'mspId': 'Org2' }},
        ],        'policy': {            '1-of': [{ 'signed-by': 0}, { 'signed-by': 1 },]
        }
    }}}
